{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeVertical","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","symbolKind":"case"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If a text’s language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"placement would be laid out vertically."}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeVertical":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If a text’s language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"placement would be laid out vertically."}],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant."}],"title":"MLNTextWritingMode","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingMode"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol"}}}